data.description: Adorable home on almost 2 acres! Fresh paint and carpet. Beautifully landscaped lot with seasonal flowers and plants. Relaxing patio among the large shade trees! Detached one car garage with great workshop space. Separate storage building. Covered front porch. Split bedroom arrangement. Formal dining could easily be a 4th bedroom. Great hardwood floors. Oversized laundry room. One year home warranty too.
